# Proxy list — copy to proxies.txt (gitignored) and populate with your proxies.
# proxies.txt is NEVER committed — it may contain credentials.
#
# Supported formats (one per line):
#   http://1.2.3.4:8080
#   https://1.2.3.4:8080
#   socks5://1.2.3.4:1080
#   http://user:password@1.2.3.4:8080
#
# Lines starting with # are ignored.
# Blank lines are ignored.
# Malformed lines are skipped with a warning.
#
# Free proxy source (dev only, low reliability):
#   config proxy refresh   — fetches from proxyscrape.com via CLI
